title: Cul Gairdin Whole Food Vegetarian Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Irish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Aside from fish, menu is vegetarian. It's a whole food cafe that serves fresh meals, salads, juices & smoothies, soups, home-style baking, organic coffee. Has vegan and gluten free options and early bird menu.
